description: Try our easy to follow Seafood Spaghetti recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Seafood pasta,Pescatarian,Tree nut free,Seafood,Low sugar,Sesame free,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,High fibre,Soy free,Peanut free
name: Seafood Spaghetti Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Cook pasta in a large saucepan of boiling, salted water according to packet instructions or until al dente. Drain, reserving 1/4 cup of cooking water.

Meanwhile, heat oil in a large frying pan over medium-high heat. Add garlic and chilli. Cook, stirring, for 1 minute or until fragrant. Add seafood and cook, stirring often, for 2-3 minutes or until warmed or cooked through.
Add pasta to pan. Squeeze over lemon juice, stir in parsley and toss to combine. Serve with parmesan.
